### `IconFont`
#### 地址
[Iconfont-阿里巴巴矢量图标库](https://www.iconfont.cn/manage/index?manage_type=myprojects&projectId=1707845)

#### 插件
- [GitHub - iconfont-cli/taro-iconfont-cli](https://github.com/iconfont-cli/taro-iconfont-cli)

#### 配置
- 将icon 添加到仓库
- 获取`Symbol`链接
- 更新`iconfont.json`
```json
{
    "symbol_url": "//at.alicdn.com/t/font_1707845_k4b717hruv.js", // Symbol url
    "save_dir": "./src/components/iconfont",
    "use_typescript": false,
    "platforms": "*",
    "use_rpx": true,
    "trim_icon_prefix": "icon",
    "default_icon_size": 18,
    "component_name": "IconFont"
}

// npx iconfont-taro 
// 更新 @/component/iconfont

```
#### 使用

- `pages`
```tsx
import Taro from "@tarojs/taro"

import IconFont from ""@/components/iconfont"

const Check = () => {
  return (
    <IconFont name="check" color="red" size={30}/>
  )
}

export default Check;

```

- `scss`
```scss
.icon {
  &::before {
    font-family: "iconfont";
    content: "\e687";
    display: inline-block;
    padding-right: 3px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    font-weight: 900;
  }
}
```

